Log files include information such as your internet protocol address, your internet service provider, your browser type and language, the time you visited our site, and which pages you visited on our site.

Changes to our Privacy Policy If we make any changes to our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page and update the Privacy Policy modification date below: This policy was last changed on September 9th, 2011.

raw_html:
Samurai Sudoku
Our Privacy Policy
Personally Identifiable Information
We do not collect personally identifiable information about the visitors to our website. We never sell your personal information to third parties.
Cookies and Web Beacons
This website does not use cookies, except to store your position when you click Save to save your current samurai sudoku progress. This website does not use web beacons.
We use third party advertisers to support our site. These advertisers may use cookies and/or web beacons when they serve advertisements on our site.
DoubleClick DART cookies
Google, as a third party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on this website.
Google's use of the DART cookie enables it to serve ads based on your visit to this site and other sites on the Internet.
You may opt out of the use of the DART cookie on all sites using this advertising by visiting http://www.google.com/privacy_ads.html
Log Files
Log file information is automatically reported by your web browser each time you view a web page. We collect and use the data contained in log files. Log files include information such as your internet protocol address, your internet service provider, your browser type and language, the time you visited our site, and which pages you visited on our site.
Changes to our Privacy Policy
If we make any changes to our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page and update the Privacy Policy modification date below:
This policy was last changed on September 9th, 2011.
